Feature: End-to-End Ixigo Bus Booking # features/e2e/e2e_test.feature:1

  @e2e
  Scenario: Complete bus booking flow till payment page           # features/e2e/e2e_test.feature:4
    Given user launches the browser                               # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:14
    When user opens ixigo homepage                                # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:29
    And user handles the homepage popup                           # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:34
    And user logs in with mobile number                           # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:39
    And user completes otp manually                               # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:47
    Then user should be logged in or login modal should be closed # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:52
    When user opens bus section                                   # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:59
    And user enters source city                                   # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:64
    And user enters destination city                              # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:69
    And user selects travel date                                  # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:74
    And user searches buses                                       # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:79
    And user applies bus filters                                  # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:84
    And user selects seat                                         # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:92
    And user continues booking                                    # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:99
    And user enters passenger details                             # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:104
    And user proceeds to payment                                  # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:117
    Then payment page should open                                 # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:122
    And user closes the browser                                   # features/steps/e2e_steps.py:129

